{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "第十五回\"角落里的神秘夫妻\"以西门吹雪为核心展开。开篇刻画西门吹雪杀人前的神圣仪式——沐浴更衣、斋戒三日，展现剑神对杀人的庄重态度。随后交代他为重回剑道巅峰，忍痛与妻儿分离的悲剧背景，点出\"月圆之夜紫禁之巅\"与叶孤城一战的往事。场景转至状元楼，司空摘星假扮西门吹雪与牛肉汤对坐，点了一桌白色素菜，引发牛肉汤对偷王之王财富的调侃。两人围绕\"混蛋与王八\"、陆小凤的绰号展开诙谐对话，最后司空摘星自称西门吹雪。角落里一对神秘老夫妻突然插话，老头能偷听远处对话，暗示武功深不可测，为后续剧情埋下悬念。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "你刚才叫了些什么东西给我们吃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你是不是聋子？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "我不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我刚才叫了些什么东西，你没有听见？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "我听见了。我只不过有点怀疑而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "怀疑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "怀疑你。怀疑你是不是那个挥金如土的偷王之王。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "据说那个偷王虽然从来不偷值钱的东西，却比谁的钱都多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "因为他偷的东西，都是别人请他去偷的。而且无论谁要请他偷东西，都要出很多很多的钱，据说有一次他为一个人去偷了一个马桶，那个人居然给了他五万两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "有没有这回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "如有一个又好看又可爱的小姑娘一定要说有这回事，我怎么能说没有？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "如果他偷一个马桶就可以赚五万两，那么这个偷王是不是已经应该很有钱了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "应该是的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "有钱的人，通常都是比较小器的人！这个人却是例外。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "何况他花钱花得就好像陆小凤一样，有时候甚至比陆小凤还花得快。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "能赚钱不是本事，能赚也能花钱才是本事。能花不赚，是个混蛋，能赚不花，是个王八！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "做混蛋好像是比做王八好一点！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "那是一定的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "所以你就是个王八，你既不是能花不赚的混蛋，也不是赚得满盘满钵的偷王，你只不过是个能赚钱而不会花钱的大王八，一个超级的大王八。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你是不是醉了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "我喝的是白水，白水怎么会让人醉？我只不过奇怪，一个只偷一只马桶就能赚五万两的人，怎么会在他和一个又好看又可爱的女人吃晚饭的时候，只叫白的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "白的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "白的菜，白的豆腐，白的馒头，白的水。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "依我看，那个不老实的老实和尚吃得都一定要比你好一点。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "只吃这种东西，哪里有力气生小和尚！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "现在我才知道那个陆小鸡为什么喜欢你了。你说话的腔调，简直就好像是跟他在一个模子里铸出来的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "他究竟是陆三蛋还是陆小鸡？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "两样都是。有时候他也是陆小鸟、陆小狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "陆小鸟的意思我明白，他飞起来的确就像是只小鸟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "哼！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "可是陆小狗我就不明白了。怎么会有人叫他陆小狗？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "因为他的鼻子比狗还灵，八千里之外有堆大便，他都能嗅得到。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "你呢？你究竟是司空摘星，还是满地吃屎？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我怎么会是满地吃屎？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "满地对司空，摘星对吃屎，字字都可以对得上。何况你吃的这些东西，也不比狗屎好吃多少。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "这次你错了。我叫这些东西吃，只因为我现在根本不是司空摘星。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "那你现在是谁？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "西门吹雪。满地对西门，吃屎对吹雪，岂非也对得很好。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对得真是好极了。已经好得够资格去吃一大堆狗屎，再挨一刀。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "刚才你是不是说我要挨一刀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "speaker_name": "司空摘星",
      "listener": "char_lao_tou",
      "text": "为什么我要挨一刀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "老头",
      "listener": "char_si_kong_zhai_xing",
      "text": "因为你不是西门吹雪。如果你是西门吹雪，我就是满地吃屎了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    }
  ],
